<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Well, two things:
<br />

<br />
1. I think the level 20 haste is around 80%.  This very rough figure comes from perusing (a rather less formal approach than parsing) my logs.  Bear in mind that most combat damage is from combat arts, not normal melee, so this isn't as awe-inspiring as it sounds.
<br />

<br />
2. Regen rates aren't so easy.  Your health/power goes up and down rather randomly - I think there may be some ongoing effects that drain power, but not sure.  Of course, I haven't really been able to test under controlled circumstances.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
